  "text": "When α = 1, this reduces to the corresponding update in Algorithm 2 given above. When α > 1, this is known as over-relaxation; when α < 1, this is known as under-relaxation. Previous works [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] suggest that the performance of ADMM can be improved significantly if one sets α ≈ 1.5.",
